PEOPLE IN THIS ROOM.

17:40.851 --> 17:43.889
THERE WAS A TRIAL.

17:43.980 --> 17:45.516
GHOSTLY FIGURES.

17:45.606 --> 17:47.722
THEY ARE STILL HERE.

17:47.817 --> 17:49.603
THEY HAVE NEVER LEFT.

17:49.694 --> 17:53.813
THEY WALK THE BUILDINGS
IN THE SQUARE OUTSIDE.

17:53.906 --> 17:56.318
YOU DIDN'T BURY THEM
DEEP ENOUGH, CAPTAIN.

17:56.409 --> 17:58.901
YOU DIDN'T COVER THEM UP
WITH ENOUGH EARTH,

17:58.995 --> 18:01.862
OR PERHAPS THE BULLETS
WERE TOO SMALL A CALIBER,

18:01.956 --> 18:03.913
OR THE FLAMES
NOT SUFFICIENTLY HOT,

18:04.000 --> 18:07.994
OR PERHAPS
THERE WASN'T ENOUGH GAS.

18:08.087 --> 18:11.796
BECKER. BECKER, WHO ARE YOU?

18:11.882 --> 18:15.420
DID YOU FORGET?

18:15.511 --> 18:19.596
TH E CARETAKER.

18:19.682 --> 18:21.923
THIS, THIS TRIAL--

18:22.018 --> 18:24.009
THE TRIAL IS OVER,
CAPTAIN LUTZE.

18:24.103 --> 18:27.937
<i>YOU HAVE BEEN FOUND GUILTY.</i>

18:28.024 --> 18:32.643
IT'S TIME
TO PRONOUNCE SENTENCE.

18:35.072 --> 18:38.315
YOU ARE GOING
TO PRONOUNCE SENTENCE?

18:38.409 --> 18:40.150
IS THAT WHAT YOU HAVE
IN MIND NOW?

18:40.244 --> 18:42.736
YOU WILL PRONOUNCE SENTENCE,

18:42.830 --> 18:46.824
AND THEN YOU SHALL
EXECUTE THAT SENTENCE?

18:46.917 --> 18:52.037
IS THAT CORRECT?
Haughs]

18:58.220 --> 19:00.348
PIGS! FILTH!

19:00.431 --> 19:03.173
YOU WILL ALL ASSEMBLE
IN THE SQUARE!

19:03.267 --> 19:06.225
YOU WILL PASS SENTENCE
ON CAPTAIN LUTZE!

19:06.312 --> 19:08.849
YOU WILL CRAWL
OUT OF YOUR GRAVES

19:08.939 --> 19:12.978
TO SEE THAT JUSTICE IS DONE!
Haughs]

19:13.069 --> 19:14.605
WHERE ARE THEY?

19:14.695 --> 19:16.072
WHERE'S THE JUDGE?

19:16.155 --> 19:17.316
WHERE'S THE JURY?

19:17.406 --> 19:18.942
WHERE'S THE EXECUTIONER?

19:19.033 --> 19:20.615
SHALL I TELL YOU
WHERE THEY ARE?

19:20.701 --> 19:22.362
IN YOUR MIND.

19:22.453 --> 19:24.490
<i>YOU'VE HATCHED THEM
OUT OF YOUR HATRED.</i>

19:24.580 --> 19:26.321
<i>YOU'VE PLANNED
YOUR VENGEANCE</i>

19:26.415 --> 19:28.702
<i>OUT OF THE CRAZY
QUILT OF YOUR IMAGINATION</i>

19:28.793 --> 19:30.875
SEWED TOGETHER
WITH THIN LITTLE THREADS

19:30.961 --> 19:32.543
OF WISHFUL THINKING!

19:32.630 --> 19:34.667
WHY DIDN'T I KILL YOU
WHEN I HAD A CHANCE?

19:34.757 --> 19:37.124
<i>WHY DIDN'T I--</i>

19:40.137 --> 19:44.051
BECKER?

19:44.141 --> 19:47.008
BECKER, I DID KILL YOU.

19:47.103 --> 19:49.765
I KILLED YOU THE NIGHT--

19:49.855 --> 19:51.516
YOU KILLED ME

19:51.607 --> 19:54.850
THE NIGHT THE AMERICANS
CAME CLOSE TO THE CAMP.

19:54.944 --> 19:57.811
<i>YOU TRIED
TO BURN IT DOWN, REMEMBER?</i>

19:57.905 --> 20:01.739
YOU TRIED TO KILL EVERYONE
WHO WAS LEFT.

20:01.826 --> 20:05.114
IN MY CASE, YOU SUCCEEDED.

20:05.204 --> 20:09.038
SO I THINKIT VVOULD BE A VVASTE
OF TIME, CAPTAIN, WOULDN'T IT-

20:09.125 --> 20:11.992
<i>A WASTE OF YOUR
PRECIOUS TIME--</i>

20:12.086 --> 20:16.751
OF THAT LITTLE TIME YOU HAVE
LEFT TO MURDER ME AGAIN?

20:16.841 --> 20:18.707
[yells]

20:18.801 --> 20:22.965
<i>[tragic music]</i>

20:23.055 --> 20:25.763
<i>(Becker)
CAPTAIN LUTZE.</i>

20:25.850 --> 20:28.763
<i>CAPTAIN LUTZE,</i>

20:28.853 --> 20:31.140
<i>YOU HAVE BEEN TRIED
AND FOUND GUILTY</i>

20:31.230 --> 20:33.972
<i>OF CRIMES AGAINST HUMANITY.</i>

20:34.066 --> 20:36.899
<i>IT IS THE UNANIMOUS
JUDGMENT OF THIS COURT</i>

20:36.944 --> 20:42.656
<i>THAT FROM THIS DAY ON,
YOU SHALL BE RENDERED INSANE.</i>

20:42.742 --> 20:45.825
WHAT IS THIS NONSENSE?

20:45.911 --> 20:47.993
WHAT IS THIS GIBBERISH?

20:48.080 --> 20:52.870
WHAT IS THIS MADNESS?

20:52.960 --> 20:54.792
<i>(Becker) AT THIS
GATE, YOU SHOT DOWN</i>

20:54.879 --> 20:56.790
HUNDREDS OF PEOPLE
WITH MACHINE GUNS.

20:56.881 --> 20:58.667
DO YOU FEEL IT
NOW, CAPTAIN?

20:58.758 --> 21:01.216
<i>DO YOU</i> FEEL <i>THE BULLETS
[machine gun firing]</i>

21:01.302 --> 21:02.792
SMASHING INTO YOUR BODY?

21:02.887 --> 21:05.128
DO YOU FEEL THE AGONY
OF TORTURED LEAD?

21:05.222 --> 21:09.682
<i>[tragic music]</i>

21:09.769 --> 21:12.932
ON THESE POSTS,
BY THE ANGUISHED HOUR

21:13.022 --> 21:16.435
YOU HUNG UP HUMAN BEINGS
TO DIE A SLOW DEATH.

21:16.525 --> 21:19.438
DO YOU FEEL
THEIR TORTURE NOW?

21:19.528 --> 21:22.145
<i>[tragic music]</i>

21:28.162 --> 21:29.869
IN THIS ROOM, CAPTAIN,

21:29.955 --> 21:32.367
THE THINGS YOU DID
TO HUMAN BEINGS

21:32.458 --> 21:34.324
ARE UNMENTIONABLE.

21:34.418 --> 21:35.795
<i>[agonized wailing]</i>

21:35.878 --> 21:40.714
HOW DOES THEIR
TORMENT FEEL?

21:40.800 --> 21:43.542
[agonized screaming]

21:43.636 --> 21:45.673
<i>[tragic music]</i>

21:50.142 --> 21:52.053
[screaming continues]

21:57.483 --> 22:01.021
CAPTAIN LUTZE,
IF YOU CAN STILL REASON,

22:01.111 --> 22:03.728
IF THERE'S STILL ANY
PORTION OF YOUR MIND

22:03.823 --> 22:07.657
THAT CAN STILL FUNCTION,
TAKE THIS THOUGHT WITH YOU.

22:07.743 --> 22:11.782
THIS IS NOT HATRED,
THIS IS RETRIBUTION.

22:11.872 --> 22:14.910
THIS IS NOT REVENGE,

22:15.000 --> 22:16.991
THIS IS JUSTICE.

22:17.086 --> 22:20.124
BUT THIS IS ONLY
THE BEGINNING, CAPTAIN.

22:20.214 --> 22:22.296
ONLY THE BEGINNING.

22:22.383 --> 22:28.129
YOUR FINAL JUDGMENT
WILL COME FROM GOD.

22:35.479 --> 22:37.265
HE'S SO FULL
OF SEDATIVES NOW

22:37.356 --> 22:39.313
HE DOESN'T EVEN KNOW
HE'S ON THE EARTH,

22:39.400 --> 22:40.982
BUT I WANT HIM
IN THE HOSPITAL,

22:41.068 --> 22:42.809
AND I WANT HIM
STRAPPED TO THE BED.

22:42.903 --> 22:44.109
DOCTOR?

22:44.196 --> 22:45.857
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM?

22:45.948 --> 22:48.690
I DROVE HIM UP HERE MYSELF
NOT TWO HOURS AGO.

22:48.784 --> 22:49.899
<i>HE WAS ALL RIGHT THEN.</i>

22:49.994 --> 22:51.701
I HAVE NO IDEA.

22:51.787 --> 22:54.779
I ONLY KNOW THAT HE IS
SCREAMING THROUGH PAIN.

22:54.874 --> 22:57.332
NO, IT'S MORE THAN PAIN,
IT'S AGONY.

22:57.418 --> 22:59.625
AND THERE ISN'T A MARK ON HIM.

22:59.712 --> 23:04.798
<i>HE'S INSANE,
A RAVING MANIAC.</i>

23:04.884 --> 23:06.625
BUT WHAT COULD HAPPEN
IN TWO HOURS

23:06.719 --> 23:09.256
TO TURN A MAN
INTO A RAVING MANIAC?

23:09.346 --> 23:13.556
THAT, SOMEBODY WILL HAVE
TO TELL ME THAT.

23:13.642 --> 23:15.349
DACHAU.

23:15.436 --> 23:19.976
<i>WHY DOES IT STILL STAND?</i>

23:20.065 --> 23:24.400
<i>WHY DO WE
KEEP IT STANDING?</i>

23:24.486 --> 23:27.899
<i>(narrator) THERE l5' AN ANSWER
TO THE DOCTORKS' QUEST/ON.</i>

23:27.990 --> 23:30.903
<i>ALL THE DACHAU-S'
