23:30.993 --> 23:33.655
<i>THE DACHAUS, THE BELSENS,
THE BUCHENWALDS,</i>

23:33.746 --> 23:37.410
<i>THE AUSCHWITZES, ALL OF THEM.
THEY MUST REMAIN STANDING</i>

23:37.499 --> 23:40.082
<i>BECAUSE THEY ARE A MONUMENT
TO A MOMENT IN TIME</i>

23:40.169 --> 23:43.537
<i>WHEN SOME MEN DECIDED TO TURN
THE EARTH INTO A GRAVEYARD.</i>

23:43.631 --> 23:45.872
<i>INTO IT, THEY SHOVELED
ALL OF THEIR REASON,</i>

23:45.966 --> 23:47.832
<i>THEIR LOGIC, THEIR KNOWLEDGE,</i>

23:47.927 --> 23:50.043
<i>BUT WORST OF ALL,
THEIR CONSCIENCE.</i>

23:50.137 --> 23:52.128
<i>AND THE MOMENT
