23:57.311 --> 23:59.803
<i>SOMETHING TO DWELL
ON AND TO REMEMBER,</i>

23:59.897 --> 24:01.888
<i>NOT ONLY
/N THE TWILIGHT</i> ZONE,

24:01.982 --> 24:06.021
